## 16. API sugerida

```http
GET /api/sat/catalogs
GET /api/sat/product-service-codes?search=&page=&limit=
GET /api/sat/unit-codes?search=&page=&limit=
GET /api/sat/payment-forms
GET /api/sat/payment-methods
GET /api/sat/cfdi-uses
GET /api/sat/tax-regimes
GET /api/sat/tax-objects
POST /api/products/{id}/fiscal-config
POST /api/customers/{id}/fiscal-config
POST /api/quotes/{id}/validate-fiscal
POST /api/quotes/{id}/prepare-invoice-payload
```

---

## 17. Estructura sugerida para validate-fiscal

### Input

```json
{
  "quote_id": "123"
}
```

### Output

```json
{
  "is_valid": false,
  "status": "fiscal_pending",
  "errors": [
    {
      "scope": "quote_item",
      "item_id": "123",
      "field": "sat_product_service_code",
      "message": "El concepto no tiene ClaveProdServ SAT."
    },
    {
      "scope": "customer",
      "field": "fiscal_regime_code",
      "message": "El cliente no tiene régimen fiscal configurado."
    }
  ],
  "warnings": [
    {
      "scope": "quote",
      "field": "payment_method_code",
      "message": "Si la cotización será pagada después, usar PPD y forma de pago 99."
    }
  ]
}
```

---

